ha \u00f6nce D\u00f6kta\u015f\u2019ta \u0130nsan Kaynaklar\u0131 birimi i\u00e7in meslek hastal\u0131klar\u0131 kay\u0131t uygulamas\u0131 ve dahili numara arama/\u00f6neri sistemi geli\u015ftirdi; Uluda\u011f \u00dcniversitesi\u2019nde y\u00fcr\u00fct\u00fclen makine \u00f6\u011frenmesi projesinde 5 bin yorum ve 20 bin kategori bilgisinin i\u015flenmesini sa\u011flayan ara\u00e7lar geli\u015ftirerek, e\u011fitim s\u00fcrelerini ciddi oranda k\u0131saltan optimizasyonlar yapt\u0131 ve ekibe yakla\u015f\u0131k 16 g\u00fcnl\u00fck zaman tasarrufu sa\u011flad\u0131. Veriyle \u00e7al\u0131\u015fmay\u0131 seven Faruk, y\u00fcksek RAM t\u00fcketen e\u011fitim kodlar\u0131n\u0131 optimize etme, veri setlerini temizleme ve etiketleme gibi g\u00f6revlerde sorumluluk alarak projelerin daha \u00f6l\u00e7eklenebilir hale gelmesine katk\u0131da bulundu.\n    Faruk\u015eeker-Yaz\u0131l\u0131m-Gelistirici-\u2026\n    Faruk\u2019un GitHub\u2019\u0131nda; hastalar i\u00e7in ila\u00e7 ve sa\u011fl\u0131k durumu takibi sunan MediMind, e-ticaret yorumlar\u0131n\u0131 analiz eden duygu analizi arac\u0131, kendi IoT altyap\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 kurdu\u011fu ak\u0131ll\u0131 ev projesi, IMAP \u00fczerinden \u00e7al\u0131\u015fan yapay zek\u00e2 destekli spam mail filtresi, yabanc\u0131 i\u00e7erik izlerken bilinmeyen kelimeleri oyunla\u015ft\u0131ran Wordly, \u00e7al\u0131\u015fan/m\u00fc\u015fteri odakl\u0131 anket platformu, makine \u00f6\u011frenmesi projeleri i\u00e7in veri temizleme servisi ve d\u00f6viz\u2013hisse senedi hareketlerini takip eden ki\u015fisel finans y\u00f6netim arac\u0131 gibi, ger\u00e7ek ihtiya\u00e7lardan do\u011fmu\u015f bir\u00e7ok proje yer al\u0131yor.\n    Faruk\u015eeker-Yaz\u0131l\u0131m-Gelistirici-\u2026\n    Teknik taraf\u0131nda Python, Django, DRF, FastAPI; frontend\u2019de Vue, Nuxt, Tailwind ve Bootstrap ile \u00e7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor. PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Redis, SQLite ve Firestore gibi veritabanlar\u0131n\u0131 aktif olarak kullan\u0131yor; Selenium, BeautifulSoup ve Scrapy ile geli\u015fmi\u015f scraping \u00e7\u00f6z\u00fcmleri \u00fcretiyor. Docker, Git, Nginx, AWS (EC2, S3), Railway, Cloudflare ve benzeri ara\u00e7larla uygulamalar\u0131n\u0131 \u00fcretim ortam\u0131na ta\u015f\u0131maya al\u0131\u015fk\u0131n. Akademik olarak Anadolu \u00dcniversitesi Bilgisayar Programc\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131 b\u00f6l\u00fcm\u00fcne devam ederken, Uluda\u011f \u00dcniversitesi Elektronik ve Otomasyon Teknolojisi b\u00f6l\u00fcm\u00fcnden mezun; bu s\u00fcre\u00e7te nesnelerin interneti, veri analizi ve makine \u00f6\u011frenmesi alanlar\u0131nda da kendini geli\u015ftirdi."}, {"role": "system", "content": "A\u015fa\u011f\u0131daki 'Context' bilgisine dayanarak cevap ver:\n    Context:\n    {context}\n\n    Soru: {question}\n    Cevap:"}, {"role": "system", "content": "A\u015fa\u011f\u0131daki 'Context' bilgisine dayanarak cevap ver:\n        Context:\n        2: # JavaScript ve Vue: Modern Frontend D\u00fcnyas\u0131na Giri\u015f\r\n\r\nFrontend d\u00fcnyas\u0131nda son y\u0131llar\u0131n iki vazge\u00e7ilmez oyuncusu: **JavaScript** ve onun \u00fczerinde y\u00fckselen modern framework\u2019ler. Bu yaz\u0131da, \u00f6zellikle **Vue.js** taraf\u0131na odaklanarak, JavaScript\u2019in temellerinin Vue ile nas\u0131l birle\u015fti\u011fini, hangi mant\u0131kla \u00e7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131 ve nereden ba\u015flaman gerekti\u011fini anlataca\u011f\u0131m.\r\n\r\n> Hedef: JavaScript bilen ya da \u00f6\u011frenmek isteyen biri olarak, Vue\u2019nun sana nas\u0131l \u201cg\u00fczel frontend\u201d kap\u0131lar\u0131 a\u00e7t\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 g\u00f6rmek.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## JavaScript Nedir, Vue Nerede Devreye Giriyor?\r\n\r\n**JavaScript**, taray\u0131c\u0131da \u00e7al\u0131\u015fan, web sayfalar\u0131na etkile\u015fim katan programlama dilidir.\r\n\u00d6rne\u011fin:\r\n\r\n* Butona t\u0131klay\u0131nca modal a\u00e7\u0131lmas\u0131\r\n* Form validasyonu\r\n* API\u2019den veri \u00e7ekip ekranda listeleme\r\n* Single Page Application (SPA) gibi daha karma\u015f\u0131k yap\u0131lar\r\n\r\nBunlar\u0131n hepsi JavaScript ile m\u00fcmk\u00fcn.\r\n\r\nAma projeler b\u00fcy\u00fcd\u00fck\u00e7e:\r\n\r\n* Dosyalar kar\u0131\u015f\u0131yor\r\n* DOM manip\u00fclasyonu zorla\u015f\u0131yor\r\n* \u201cBu butona t\u0131klay\u0131nca \u015funu yap, sonra oray\u0131 de\u011fi\u015ftir, sonra \u015furay\u0131 g\u00fcncelle\u201d zinciri kontrolden \u00e7\u0131k\u0131yor\r\n\r\nTam bu noktada modern framework\u2019ler devreye giriyor.\r\n**Vue.js**, bu framework\u2019lerden biri ve \u00f6zellikle:\r\n\r\n* \u00d6\u011frenmesi g\u00f6rece kolay\r\n* Dok\u00fcmantasyonu temiz\r\n* React kadar g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fc\r\n* K\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck projeden b\u00fcy\u00fck projeye kadar rahatl\u0131kla \u00f6l\u00e7eklenebilen\r\n\r\nbir yap\u0131 sunuyor.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Vue\u2019yu Anlamak \u0130\u00e7in Bilmen Gereken JavaScript Konular\u0131\r\n\r\nVue \u00f6\u011frenmeden \u00f6nce \u015fu JS konular\u0131na **en az\u0131ndan temel d\u00fczeyde** hakim olman \u00e7ok i\u015fini kolayla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r:\r\n\r\n* `let`, `const`, scope kavram\u0131\r\n* Temel veri tipleri (string, number, array, object)\r\n* Fonksiyonlar (\u00f6zellikle arrow functions: `() => {}`)\r\n* `this` mant\u0131\u011f\u0131 (Vue 2 kullanacaksan \u00e7ok \u00f6nemli, Vue 3\u2019te Composition API ile biraz de\u011fi\u015fiyor)\r\n* Promise ve `async/await`\r\n* ES Modules (`import`, `export`)\r\n\r\n\u00d6rne\u011fin:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst users = [\r\n  { id: 1, name: \"Ali\" },\r\n  { id: 2, name: \"Ay\u015fe\" },\r\n];\r\n\r\nconst names = users.map((user) => user.name);\r\nconsole.log(names); // [\"Ali\", \"Ay\u015fe\"]\r\n```\r\n\r\nVue ile \u00e7al\u0131\u015f\u0131rken:\r\n\r\n* API\u2019den veri \u00e7ekip state\u2019e atarken\r\n* Liste render ederken (`v-for`)\r\n* Computed property veya method yazarken\r\n\r\nbunlar\u0131n hepsinde bu tarz temel JS bilgilerini kullanacaks\u0131n.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Vue.js Nedir? K\u0131saca Felsefesini Anlayal\u0131m\r\n\r\nVue\u2019nun olay\u0131 \u015fu:\r\n\r\n> \u201cSen veriyi tan\u0131mla, HTML\u2019in veriden otomatik g\u00fcncellensin.\u201d\r\n\r\nYani klasik DOM manip\u00fclasyonu yerine reaktif bir yakla\u015f\u0131m sunuyor.\r\n\u00d6rne\u011fin:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<div id=\"app\">\r\n  <p>{{ message }}</p>\r\n  <button @click=\"changeMessage\">Mesaj\u0131 De\u011fi\u015ftir</button>\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst { createApp } = Vue;\r\n\r\ncreateApp({\r\n  data() {\r\n    return {\r\n      message: \"Merhaba Vue!\",\r\n    };\r\n  },\r\n  methods: {\r\n    changeMessage() {\r\n      this.message = \"Mesaj g\u00fcncellendi!\";\r\n    },\r\n  },\r\n}).mount(\"#app\");\r\n```\r\n\r\nBurada:\r\n\r\n* `message` de\u011fi\u015fti\u011fi anda Vue DOM\u2019u kendisi g\u00fcncelliyor.\r\n* Sen `document.querySelector` ile u\u011fra\u015fm\u0131yorsun.\r\n* JavaScript state\u2019in ile HTML DOM aras\u0131nda **otomatik senkronizasyon** var.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## En Basit Vue Uygulamas\u0131 (CDN ile Ba\u015flang\u0131\u00e7)\r\n\r\nHerhangi bir build arac\u0131 kurmadan Vue denemek istiyorsan, CDN ile ba\u015flayabilirsin.\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"tr\">\r\n  <head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\r\n    <title>Vue Counter</title>\r\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/vue@3/dist/vue.global.js\"></script>\r\n  </head>\r\n  <body>\r\n    <div id=\"app\">\r\n      <h1>Counter: {{ counter }}</h1>\r\n      <button @click=\"counter++\">Artt\u0131r</button>\r\n      <button @click=\"counter--\">Azalt</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <script>\r\n      const { createApp } = Vue;\r\n\r\n      createApp({\r\n        data() {\r\n          return {\r\n            counter: 0,\r\n          };\r\n        },\r\n      }).mount(\"#app\");\r\n    </script>\r\n  </body>\r\n</html>\r\n```\r\n\r\nBurada dikkat edilecek \u015feyler:\r\n\r\n* `{{ counter }}` \u2192 Vue\u2019nun template syntax\u2019\u0131 (interpolation)\r\n* `@click` \u2192 Event binding (k\u0131saltma: `v-on:click`)\r\n* `data()` fonksiyonu \u2192 Component\u2019in state\u2019ini d\u00f6nd\u00fcr\u00fcyor\r\n\r\nBu kadar basit bir setup ile bile JavaScript + Vue birlikteli\u011fini hissedebilirsin.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Single File Component (SFC) ve Modern Vue Geli\u015ftirme\r\n\r\nGer\u00e7ek projelerde CDN ile tek HTML dosyas\u0131na Vue g\u00f6mmek pek kullan\u0131lm\u0131yor. Onun yerine:\r\n\r\n* `Vite` veya `Vue CLI` ile proje ba\u015flat\u0131l\u0131r\r\n* Her component `.vue` dosyas\u0131 olarak yaz\u0131l\u0131r\r\n* \u0130\u00e7inde `<template>`, `<script>`, `<style>` b\u00f6l\u00fcmleri olur\r\n\r\n\u00d6rnek bir `Counter.vue` component\u2019i:\r\n\r\n```vue\r\n<template>\r\n  <div>\r\n    <h2>Counter: {{ count }}</h2>\r\n    <button @click=\"increment\">+1</button>\r\n  </div>\r\n</template>\r\n\r\n<script setup>\r\nimport { ref } from \"vue\";\r\n\r\nconst count = ref(0);\r\n\r\nfunction increment() {\r\n  count.value++;\r\n}\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<style scoped>\r\nbutton {\r\n  padding: 0.5rem 1rem;\r\n  border-radius: 8px;\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n```\r\n\r\n\u00d6nemli noktalar:\r\n\r\n* `script setup` \u2192 Vue 3 ile gelen sade, modern Composition API kullan\u0131m \u015fekli\r\n* `ref()` \u2192 Reaktif de\u011fi\u015fken tan\u0131mlamak i\u00e7in kullan\u0131l\u0131yor\r\n* `count.value` \u2192 Reaktif de\u011fi\u015fkenin ger\u00e7ek de\u011feri (script k\u0131sm\u0131nda b\u00f6yle kullan\u0131l\u0131yor)\r\n* `scoped` \u2192 CSS\u2019in sadece bu componente uygulanmas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011flar\r\n\r\nBu yap\u0131 sayesinde:\r\n\r\n* HTML, JS, CSS **ayn\u0131 dosya i\u00e7inde**, tek bir component mant\u0131\u011f\u0131yla y\u00f6netiliyor.\r\n* B\u00fcy\u00fck projelerde bile d\u00fczenli kalmak \u00e7ok daha kolay.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Vue \u0130\u00e7inde State Y\u00f6netimi: Basit JS\u2019ten Pinia\u2019ya\r\n\r\nK\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck projelerde state \u00e7o\u011funlukla component i\u00e7inde tutulur.\r\nBiraz b\u00fcy\u00fcy\u00fcnce:\r\n\r\n* Ayn\u0131 veriyi birden \u00e7ok component kullanmak ister\r\n* \u201cProps ile a\u015fa\u011f\u0131, event ile yukar\u0131\u201d derken kafa kar\u0131\u015fmaya ba\u015flar\r\n\r\nBu noktada, Vue ekosisteminde iki pop\u00fcler \u00e7\u00f6z\u00fcm var:\r\n\r\n* Eski nesil: Vuex\r\n* Modern ve hafif: **Pinia**\r\n\r\n\u00d6rne\u011fin Pinia ile \u00e7ok basit bir store:\r\n\r\n```js\r\n// stores/counter.js\r\nimport { defineStore } from \"pinia\";\r\n\r\nexport const useCounterStore = defineStore(\"counter\", {\r\n  state: () => ({\r\n    count: 0,\r\n  }),\r\n  actions: {\r\n    increment() {\r\n      this.count++;\r\n    },\r\n  },\r\n});\r\n```\r\n\r\nComponent i\u00e7inde kullan\u0131m\u0131:\r\n\r\n```vue\r\n<script setup>\r\nimport { useCounterStore } from \"@/stores/counter\";\r\n\r\nconst counter = useCounterStore();\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<template>\r\n  <div>\r\n    <p>Counter: {{ counter.count }}</p>\r\n    <button @click=\"counter.increment()\">+1</button>\r\n  </div>\r\n</template>\r\n```\r\n\r\nBurada olan \u015fey asl\u0131nda:\r\n\r\n* JavaScript ile global bir \u201cstate objesi\u201d olu\u015fturuyorsun\r\n* Vue ve Pinia bunu reaktif hale getirip component\u2019lerle ba\u011flayor\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## JavaScript + Vue ile \u00c7al\u0131\u015f\u0131rken Dikkat Etmen Gereken Noktalar\r\n\r\n1. **JS Temelini Hafife Alma**\r\n   Vue, JavaScript\u2019i saklam\u0131yor, aksine **daha \u00e7ok kullanman\u0131** sa\u011fl\u0131yor.\r\n   Ne kadar iyi JS bilirsen, Vue ile o kadar rahat edersin.\r\n\r\n2. **Reaktivite Mant\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 Anla**\r\n   Vue\u2019da \u201cde\u011fi\u015fken de\u011fi\u015ftirdim, DOM otomatik g\u00fcncellendi\u201d b\u00fcy\u00fc gibi gelebilir.\r\n   Ama bunun arkas\u0131nda reaktivite sistemi var. \u00d6zellikle `ref`, `reactive`, `computed`, `watch` gibi kavramlar\u0131 sindir.\r\n\r\n3. **Component Mant\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 Benimse**\r\n   Bir sayfay\u0131:\r\n\r\n   * Header component\r\n   * Sidebar component\r\n   * Content component\r\n   * Footer component\r\n     gibi par\u00e7alara ay\u0131rmak, hem JS hem HTML taraf\u0131nda temiz bir yap\u0131 sa\u011flar.\r\n\r\n4. **Temiz Dosya Yap\u0131s\u0131 Kur**\r\n   API servislerini `services/`, global state\u2019i `stores/`, reusable component\u2019leri `components/` dizinine al.\r\n   Bu asl\u0131nda JavaScript mod\u00fcllerini mant\u0131kl\u0131 klas\u00f6rlere ay\u0131rmaktan ibaret.\r\n\r\n5. **TypeScript D\u00fc\u015f\u00fcn (\u0130leri Seviyede)**\r\n   Vue, TypeScript ile \u00e7ok iyi \u00e7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor. JavaScript temelin oturduktan sonra TS \u00f6\u011frenmek, \u00f6zellikle b\u00fcy\u00fck projelerde sana ciddi g\u00fc\u00e7 kazand\u0131r\u0131r.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Nereden Ba\u015flamal\u0131?\r\n\r\nBa\u015flang\u0131\u00e7 i\u00e7in \u00f6neri yol haritas\u0131:\r\n\r\n1. **Saf JavaScript ile mini projeler yap**\r\n\r\n   * Todo list\r\n   * Basit fetch ile API\u2019den veri \u00e7ekip listeleme\r\n   * Modal a\u00e7-kapat\r\n\r\n2. **Vue\u2019yu CDN ile dene**\r\n\r\n   * Tek HTML dosyas\u0131nda Vue ekle\r\n   * `data`, `methods`, `v-for`, `v-if`, `v-model` gibi temel direktifleri kullan\r\n\r\n3. **Vite ile Vue 3 projesi a\u00e7**\r\n\r\n   ```bash\r\n   npm create vite@latest my-vue-app -- --template vue\r\n   cd my-vue-app\r\n   npm install\r\n   npm run dev\r\n   ```\r\n\r\n4. **Component ve `script setup` yap\u0131s\u0131na al\u0131\u015f**\r\n\r\n   * K\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck component\u2019ler yaz\r\n   * Props ve emit (event) kullan\r\n\r\n5. **Pinia ile basit bir global state yaz**\r\n\r\n   * Login state, counter, theme vs. gibi basit \u015feylerle ba\u015fla\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Son S\u00f6z\r\n\r\nJavaScript ve Vue ili\u015fkisi asl\u0131nda \u015fu \u015fekilde \u00f6zetlenebilir:\r\n\r\n> JavaScript, beynin. Vue, o beyni kullanarak **d\u00fczenli, reaktif, component tabanl\u0131** aray\u00fczler \u00e7izmeni sa\u011flayan iskelet.\r\n\r\nJS temelin ne kadar sa\u011flam olursa, Vue \u00f6\u011frenmek ve \u00f6zellikle ileri seviye \u00f6zelliklerine (Composition API, Pinia, Router, SSR, PWA vs.) ge\u00e7mek o kadar h\u0131zl\u0131 olur.\n1: ## Django ile Web Geli\u015ftirmeye Ba\u015flamak\r\n\r\n*\u201cBatteries included\u201d framework ile \u00fcretkenlik patlamas\u0131*\r\n\r\nDjango\u2019yu bir c\u00fcmleyle \u00f6zetle deseler, \u015f\u00f6yle derdim:\r\n\r\n> Az kodla, temiz mimariyle, \u00e7ok h\u0131zl\u0131 web uygulamas\u0131 geli\u015ftirmek istiyorsan, Django tam senlik.\r\n\r\nBu yaz\u0131da:\r\n\r\n* Django\u2019nun ne oldu\u011funu\r\n* MTV (Model\u2013Template\u2013View) mimarisini\r\n* K\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck bir proje iskeletini\r\n* Model, view, template ak\u0131\u015f\u0131n\u0131\r\n* Admin paneli ve migration mant\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131\r\n\r\nk\u0131saca ama net bir \u015fekilde anlataca\u011f\u0131m.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Django nedir, ne zaman i\u015fine yarar?\r\n\r\nDjango, Python ile yaz\u0131lm\u0131\u015f, **y\u00fcksek seviyeli bir web framework**. Hedefi:\r\n\r\n* Tekrar eden i\u015fleri senin yerine halletmek\r\n* \u201cBest practice\u201d mimariye seni zorla yakla\u015ft\u0131rmak\r\n* G\u00fcvenlik, performans, \u00f6l\u00e7eklenebilirlik gibi dertleri m\u00fcmk\u00fcn oldu\u011funca kolayla\u015ft\u0131rmak\r\n\r\nDjango \u015fu tarz projeler i\u00e7in \u00e7ok uygun:\r\n\r\n* Klasik web siteleri (blog, kurumsal site, portal)\r\n* Dashboard, panel, admin sayfalar\u0131\r\n* CRUD tabanl\u0131 uygulamalar (todo app, proje y\u00f6netimi, stok takibi)\r\n* API tabanl\u0131 backend (DRF ile birlikte)\r\n\r\nE\u011fer:\r\n\r\n* SQL ile u\u011fra\u015fmak istemiyor,\r\n* Auth, permission, admin panel gibi \u015feyleri s\u0131f\u0131rdan yazmak istemiyorsan,\r\n\r\nDjango sana \u00e7ok zaman kazand\u0131r\u0131r.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Django\u2019nun MTV Mimarisi\r\n\r\nDjango, klasik MVC\u2019ye \u00e7ok benzer ama isimlendirmesi farkl\u0131d\u0131r: **MTV**\r\n\r\n* **Model** \u2192 Veritaban\u0131 katman\u0131\r\n* **Template** \u2192 HTML katman\u0131 (frontend)\r\n* **View** \u2192 Request\u2019i al\u0131r, veriyi i\u015fler, uygun template\u2019i d\u00f6nd\u00fcr\u00fcr\r\n\r\nAk\u0131\u015f kabaca \u015f\u00f6yle:\r\n\r\n1. Kullan\u0131c\u0131 bir URL\u2019e istek atar\r\n2. `urls.py` o iste\u011fi ilgili view\u2019e y\u00f6nlendirir\r\n3. View, gerekirse Model\u2019den veri \u00e7eker\r\n4. View veriyi Template\u2019e g\u00f6nderir\r\n5. Template HTML \u00fcretir, kullan\u0131c\u0131ya d\u00f6ner\r\n\r\nBu ayr\u0131m, kodun **daha okunabilir** ve **bak\u0131m\u0131 kolay** olmas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011flar.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Basit bir blog projesi: \u0130skelet\r\n\r\n\u00d6rnek \u00fczerinden gidelim:\r\nMinik bir \u201cBlog\u201d projesi kurmak istiyoruz.\r\n\r\n### 1. Proje ve app olu\u015fturma\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# Sanal ortam \u00f6nerilir\r\npython -m venv venv\r\nsource venv/bin/activate  # Windows: venv\\Scripts\\activate\r\n\r\npip install django\r\n\r\ndjango-admin startproject myblog\r\ncd myblog\r\npython manage.py startapp blog\r\n```\r\n\r\n`settings.py` i\u00e7inde `INSTALLED_APPS` b\u00f6l\u00fcm\u00fcne `blog` app\u2019ini eklemeyi unutma:\r\n\r\n```python\r\nINSTALLED_APPS = [\r\n    # ...\r\n    \"blog\",\r\n]\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Model: Yaz\u0131lar\u0131 Tan\u0131mlayal\u0131m\r\n\r\nBlog yaz\u0131lar\u0131m\u0131z i\u00e7in basit bir model:\r\n\r\n```python\r\n# blog/models.py\r\nfrom django.db import models\r\n\r\nclass Post(models.Model):\r\n    title = models.CharField(max_length=200)      # Post title\r\n    slug = models.SlugField(unique=True)         # SEO-friendly URL key\r\n    content = models.TextField()                 # Post body\r\n    created_at = models.DateTimeField(auto_now_add=True)  # First created date\r\n    updated_at = models.DateTimeField(auto_now=True)      # Last updated date\r\n    is_published = models.BooleanField(default=True)      # Draft / Published\r\n\r\n    def __str__(self):\r\n        return self.title\r\n```\r\n\r\n> Not: `auto_now_add` / `auto_now` alanlar\u0131, tarihleri otomatik y\u00f6neterek ekstra kod yazman\u0131 engeller.\r\n\r\nModeli yazd\u0131ktan sonra:\r\n\r\n```bash\r\npython manage.py makemigrations\r\npython manage.py migrate\r\n```\r\n\r\nBu komutlar veritaban\u0131nda tabloyu olu\u015fturur.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Admin Paneli: Out-of-the-box Y\u00f6netim\r\n\r\nDjango\u2019nun en tatl\u0131 yanlar\u0131ndan biri: **Admin paneli**.\r\n\r\n```python\r\n# blog/admin.py\r\nfrom django.contrib import admin\r\nfrom .models import Post\r\n\r\n@admin.register(Post)\r\nclass PostAdmin(admin.ModelAdmin):\r\n    list_display = (\"title\", \"is_published\", \"created_at\")\r\n    prepopulated_fields = {\"slug\": (\"title\",)}\r\n```\r\n\r\nArd\u0131ndan bir s\u00fcper kullan\u0131c\u0131 olu\u015ftur:\r\n\r\n```bash\r\npython manage.py createsuperuser\r\npython manage.py runserver\r\n```\r\n\r\n`/admin` sayfas\u0131na girerek Post\u2019lar\u0131 web aray\u00fcz\u00fcnden ekleyebilir, d\u00fczenleyebilirsin.\r\nKod yazmadan CRUD yapmak = \u00fcretkenlik boost.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## View: Veriyi Al, \u015eablona G\u00f6nder\r\n\r\nBasit bir \u201clistele ve detay\u201d ak\u0131\u015f\u0131 kural\u0131m.\r\n\r\n```python\r\n# blog/views.py\r\nfrom django.shortcuts import render, get_object_or_404\r\nfrom .models import Post\r\n\r\ndef post_list(request):\r\n    posts = Post.objects.filter(is_published=True).order_by(\"-created_at\")  # Latest first\r\n    return render(request, \"blog/post_list.html\", {\"posts\": posts})\r\n\r\ndef post_detail(request, slug):\r\n    post = get_object_or_404(Post, slug=slug, is_published=True)\r\n    return render(request, \"blog/post_detail.html\", {\"post\": post})\r\n```\r\n\r\n> Not: `get_object_or_404`, obje bulunamazsa otomatik 404 d\u00f6nd\u00fcrerek hata y\u00f6netimini basitle\u015ftirir.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## URL\u2019ler: Kullan\u0131c\u0131y\u0131 Do\u011fru View\u2019e Y\u00f6nlendirme\r\n\r\n\u00d6nce app i\u00e7i `urls.py`:\r\n\r\n```python\r\n# blog/urls.py\r\nfrom django.urls import path\r\nfrom . import views\r\n\r\nurlpatterns = [\r\n    path(\"\", views.post_list, name=\"post_list\"),\r\n    path(\"<slug:slug>/\", views.post_detail, name=\"post_detail\"),\r\n]\r\n```\r\n\r\nSonra proje `urls.py` i\u00e7ine include et:\r\n\r\n```python\r\n# myblog/urls.py\r\nfrom django.contrib import admin\r\nfrom django.urls import path, include\r\n\r\nurlpatterns = [\r\n    path(\"admin/\", admin.site.urls),\r\n    path(\"\", include(\"blog.urls\")),\r\n]\r\n```\r\n\r\nArt\u0131k:\r\n\r\n* `http://localhost:8000/` \u2192 Post listesi\r\n* `http://localhost:8000/baz\u0131-yazi-slug/` \u2192 Yaz\u0131 detay\u0131\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Template: HTML ile Bulu\u015fma\r\n\r\nBasit template \u00f6rnekleri:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<!-- templates/blog/post_list.html -->\r\n<!doctype html>\r\n<html>\r\n  <head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\r\n    <title>My Blog</title>\r\n  </head>\r\n  <body>\r\n    <h1>Blog</h1>\r\n    <ul>\r\n      {% for post in posts %}\r\n        <li>\r\n          <a href=\"{{ post.slug }}/\">{{ post.title }}</a>\r\n          <small>{{ post.created_at }}</small>\r\n        </li>\r\n      {% empty %}\r\n        <li>No posts yet.</li>\r\n      {% endfor %}\r\n    </ul>\r\n  </body>\r\n</html>\r\n```\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<!-- templates/blog/post_detail.html -->\r\n<!doctype html>\r\n<html>\r\n  <head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\r\n    <title>{{ post.title }}</title>\r\n  </head>\r\n  <body>\r\n    <a href=\"/\">\u2190 Back</a>\r\n    <h1>{{ post.title }}</h1>\r\n    <p>{{ post.created_at }}</p>\r\n    <div>\r\n      {{ post.content|linebreaks }}  <!-- Converts newlines to <p>/<br> -->\r\n    </div>\r\n  </body>\r\n</html>\r\n```\r\n\r\n> Not: Django template dili, hem basit hem de g\u00fcvenli; HTML i\u00e7inde Python yazd\u0131rmana izin vermeden veriyi kontrol alt\u0131nda tutar.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Django\u2019nun G\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fc Oldu\u011fu Noktalar\r\n\r\nDjango\u2019yu \u201cframework se\u00e7erken\u201d \u00f6ne \u00e7\u0131karan \u015feyler:\r\n\r\n* **Built-in Auth**: User, login, logout, permission, group vs.\r\n* **ORM**: SQL yazmadan \u00e7o\u011fu i\u015fi halledebilirsin, gerekti\u011finde raw SQL de destekler\r\n* **Admin Panel**: MVP ve paneller i\u00e7in muazzam h\u0131z kazand\u0131r\u0131r\r\n* **Security**: CSRF, XSS, SQL Injection gibi yayg\u0131n g\u00fcvenlik sorunlar\u0131na kar\u015f\u0131 g\u00f6m\u00fcl\u00fc korumalar\r\n* **Ecosystem**: Django REST Framework, django-allauth, Celery integration, vs.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Ne Zaman Django Kullanma?\r\n\r\nHer ara\u00e7 her i\u015f i\u00e7in de\u011fil. Django\u2019yu **\u015fu durumlarda** d\u00fc\u015f\u00fcnmeyebilirsin:\r\n\r\n* \u00c7ok hafif, tek endpoint\u2019lik bir API yaz\u0131yorsun\r\n* Microservice yap\u0131s\u0131nda, ultra minimal bir servis istiyorsun\r\n* High-performance, ultra low-level kontrol istiyorsun (\u00f6rne\u011fin bare ASGI veya FastAPI + \u00f6zel tuning)\r\n\r\nAma klasik web uygulamalar\u0131, dashboard, portal, admin tarz\u0131 i\u015fler i\u00e7in Django \u00e7o\u011fu zaman **fazlas\u0131yla yeterli ve h\u0131zl\u0131**.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Sonu\u00e7: Neden Bug\u00fcn Ba\u015flamal\u0131s\u0131n?\r\n\r\nDjango:\r\n\r\n* Python bilgini direkt prati\u011fe d\u00f6kmeni sa\u011flar\r\n* Seni ba\u015ftan iyi bir mimariye zorlar\r\n* \u201c\u00d6nce \u00e7al\u0131\u015fan bir \u00fcr\u00fcn \u00e7\u0131karay\u0131m\u201d diyorsan MVP s\u00fcrecini ciddi anlamda h\u0131zland\u0131r\u0131r\r\n\r\nE\u011fer elinde:\r\n\r\n* Basit bir blog fikri\r\n* Bir \u00fcr\u00fcn i\u00e7in admin panel ihtiyac\u0131\r\n* M\u00fc\u015fteriye h\u0131zl\u0131 bir prototip \u00e7\u0131karma iste\u011fi\r\n\r\nvarsa, bug\u00fcn bir Django projesi a\u00e7\u0131p, 1\u20132 saat i\u00e7inde \u00e7al\u0131\u015fan bir \u015fey ortaya koyabilirsin.\n2: # JavaScript ve Vue: Modern Frontend D\u00fcnyas\u0131na Giri\u015f\r\n\r\nFrontend d\u00fcnyas\u0131nda son y\u0131llar\u0131n iki vazge\u00e7ilmez oyuncusu: **JavaScript** ve onun \u00fczerinde y\u00fckselen modern framework\u2019ler. Bu yaz\u0131da, \u00f6zellikle **Vue.js** taraf\u0131na odaklanarak, JavaScript\u2019in temellerinin Vue ile nas\u0131l birle\u015fti\u011fini, hangi mant\u0131kla \u00e7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131 ve nereden ba\u015flaman gerekti\u011fini anlataca\u011f\u0131m.\r\n\r\n> Hedef: JavaScript bilen ya da \u00f6\u011frenmek isteyen biri olarak, Vue\u2019nun sana nas\u0131l \u201cg\u00fczel frontend\u201d kap\u0131lar\u0131 a\u00e7t\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 g\u00f6rmek.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## JavaScript Nedir, Vue Nerede Devreye Giriyor?\r\n\r\n**JavaScript**, taray\u0131c\u0131da \u00e7al\u0131\u015fan, web sayfalar\u0131na etkile\u015fim katan programlama dilidir.\r\n\u00d6rne\u011fin:\r\n\r\n* Butona t\u0131klay\u0131nca modal a\u00e7\u0131lmas\u0131\r\n* Form validasyonu\r\n* API\u2019den veri \u00e7ekip ekranda listeleme\r\n* Single Page Application (SPA) gibi daha karma\u015f\u0131k yap\u0131lar\r\n\r\nBunlar\u0131n hepsi JavaScript ile m\u00fcmk\u00fcn.\r\n\r\nAma projeler b\u00fcy\u00fcd\u00fck\u00e7e:\r\n\r\n* Dosyalar kar\u0131\u015f\u0131yor\r\n* DOM manip\u00fclasyonu zorla\u015f\u0131yor\r\n* \u201cBu butona t\u0131klay\u0131nca \u015funu yap, sonra oray\u0131 de\u011fi\u015ftir, sonra \u015furay\u0131 g\u00fcncelle\u201d zinciri kontrolden \u00e7\u0131k\u0131yor\r\n\r\nTam bu noktada modern framework\u2019ler devreye giriyor.\r\n**Vue.js**, bu framework\u2019lerden biri ve \u00f6zellikle:\r\n\r\n* \u00d6\u011frenmesi g\u00f6rece kolay\r\n* Dok\u00fcmantasyonu temiz\r\n* React kadar g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fc\r\n* K\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck projeden b\u00fcy\u00fck projeye kadar rahatl\u0131kla \u00f6l\u00e7eklenebilen\r\n\r\nbir yap\u0131 sunuyor.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Vue\u2019yu Anlamak \u0130\u00e7in Bilmen Gereken JavaScript Konular\u0131\r\n\r\nVue \u00f6\u011frenmeden \u00f6nce \u015fu JS konular\u0131na **en az\u0131ndan temel d\u00fczeyde** hakim olman \u00e7ok i\u015fini kolayla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r:\r\n\r\n* `let`, `const`, scope kavram\u0131\r\n* Temel veri tipleri (string, number, array, object)\r\n* Fonksiyonlar (\u00f6zellikle arrow functions: `() => {}`)\r\n* `this` mant\u0131\u011f\u0131 (Vue 2 kullanacaksan \u00e7ok \u00f6nemli, Vue 3\u2019te Composition API ile biraz de\u011fi\u015fiyor)\r\n* Promise ve `async/await`\r\n* ES Modules (`import`, `export`)\r\n\r\n\u00d6rne\u011fin:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst users = [\r\n  { id: 1, name: \"Ali\" },\r\n  { id: 2, name: \"Ay\u015fe\" },\r\n];\r\n\r\nconst names = users.map((user) => user.name);\r\nconsole.log(names); // [\"Ali\", \"Ay\u015fe\"]\r\n```\r\n\r\nVue ile \u00e7al\u0131\u015f\u0131rken:\r\n\r\n* API\u2019den veri \u00e7ekip state\u2019e atarken\r\n* Liste render ederken (`v-for`)\r\n* Computed property veya method yazarken\r\n\r\nbunlar\u0131n hepsinde bu tarz temel JS bilgilerini kullanacaks\u0131n.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Vue.js Nedir? K\u0131saca Felsefesini Anlayal\u0131m\r\n\r\nVue\u2019nun olay\u0131 \u015fu:\r\n\r\n> \u201cSen veriyi tan\u0131mla, HTML\u2019in veriden otomatik g\u00fcncellensin.\u201d\r\n\r\nYani klasik DOM manip\u00fclasyonu yerine reaktif bir yakla\u015f\u0131m sunuyor.\r\n\u00d6rne\u011fin:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<div id=\"app\">\r\n  <p>{{ message }}</p>\r\n  <button @click=\"changeMessage\">Mesaj\u0131 De\u011fi\u015ftir</button>\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst { createApp } = Vue;\r\n\r\ncreateApp({\r\n  data() {\r\n    return {\r\n      message: \"Merhaba Vue!\",\r\n    };\r\n  },\r\n  methods: {\r\n    changeMessage() {\r\n      this.message = \"Mesaj g\u00fcncellendi!\";\r\n    },\r\n  },\r\n}).mount(\"#app\");\r\n```\r\n\r\nBurada:\r\n\r\n* `message` de\u011fi\u015fti\u011fi anda Vue DOM\u2019u kendisi g\u00fcncelliyor.\r\n* Sen `document.querySelector` ile u\u011fra\u015fm\u0131yorsun.\r\n* JavaScript state\u2019in ile HTML DOM aras\u0131nda **otomatik senkronizasyon** var.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## En Basit Vue Uygulamas\u0131 (CDN ile Ba\u015flang\u0131\u00e7)\r\n\r\nHerhangi bir build arac\u0131 kurmadan Vue denemek istiyorsan, CDN ile ba\u015flayabilirsin.\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"tr\">\r\n  <head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\r\n    <title>Vue Counter</title>\r\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/vue@3/dist/vue.global.js\"></script>\r\n  </head>\r\n  <body>\r\n    <div id=\"app\">\r\n      <h1>Counter: {{ counter }}</h1>\r\n      <button @click=\"counter++\">Artt\u0131r</button>\r\n      <button @click=\"counter--\">Azalt</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <script>\r\n      const { createApp } = Vue;\r\n\r\n      createApp({\r\n        data() {\r\n          return {\r\n            counter: 0,\r\n          };\r\n        },\r\n      }).mount(\"#app\");\r\n    </script>\r\n  </body>\r\n</html>\r\n```\r\n\r\nBurada dikkat edilecek \u015feyler:\r\n\r\n* `{{ counter }}` \u2192 Vue\u2019nun template syntax\u2019\u0131 (interpolation)\r\n* `@click` \u2192 Event binding (k\u0131saltma: `v-on:click`)\r\n* `data()` fonksiyonu \u2192 Component\u2019in state\u2019ini d\u00f6nd\u00fcr\u00fcyor\r\n\r\nBu kadar basit bir setup ile bile JavaScript + Vue birlikteli\u011fini hissedebilirsin.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Single File Component (SFC) ve Modern Vue Geli\u015ftirme\r\n\r\nGer\u00e7ek projelerde CDN ile tek HTML dosyas\u0131na Vue g\u00f6mmek pek kullan\u0131lm\u0131yor. Onun yerine:\r\n\r\n* `Vite` veya `Vue CLI` ile proje ba\u015flat\u0131l\u0131r\r\n* Her component `.vue` dosyas\u0131 olarak yaz\u0131l\u0131r\r\n* \u0130\u00e7inde `<template>`, `<script>`, `<style>` b\u00f6l\u00fcmleri olur\r\n\r\n\u00d6rnek bir `Counter.vue` component\u2019i:\r\n\r\n```vue\r\n<template>\r\n  <div>\r\n    <h2>Counter: {{ count }}</h2>\r\n    <button @click=\"increment\">+1</button>\r\n  </div>\r\n</template>\r\n\r\n<script setup>\r\nimport { ref } from \"vue\";\r\n\r\nconst count = ref(0);\r\n\r\nfunction increment() {\r\n  count.value++;\r\n}\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<style scoped>\r\nbutton {\r\n  padding: 0.5rem 1rem;\r\n  border-radius: 8px;\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n```\r\n\r\n\u00d6nemli noktalar:\r\n\r\n* `script setup` \u2192 Vue 3 ile gelen sade, modern Composition API kullan\u0131m \u015fekli\r\n* `ref()` \u2192 Reaktif de\u011fi\u015fken tan\u0131mlamak i\u00e7in kullan\u0131l\u0131yor\r\n* `count.value` \u2192 Reaktif de\u011fi\u015fkenin ger\u00e7ek de\u011feri (script k\u0131sm\u0131nda b\u00f6yle kullan\u0131l\u0131yor)\r\n* `scoped` \u2192 CSS\u2019in sadece bu componente uygulanmas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011flar\r\n\r\nBu yap\u0131 sayesinde:\r\n\r\n* HTML, JS, CSS **ayn\u0131 dosya i\u00e7inde**, tek bir component mant\u0131\u011f\u0131yla y\u00f6netiliyor.\r\n* B\u00fcy\u00fck projelerde bile d\u00fczenli kalmak \u00e7ok daha kolay.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Vue \u0130\u00e7inde State Y\u00f6netimi: Basit JS\u2019ten Pinia\u2019ya\r\n\r\nK\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck projelerde state \u00e7o\u011funlukla component i\u00e7inde tutulur.\r\nBiraz b\u00fcy\u00fcy\u00fcnce:\r\n\r\n* Ayn\u0131 veriyi birden \u00e7ok component kullanmak ister\r\n* \u201cProps ile a\u015fa\u011f\u0131, event ile yukar\u0131\u201d derken kafa kar\u0131\u015fmaya ba\u015flar\r\n\r\nBu noktada, Vue ekosisteminde iki pop\u00fcler \u00e7\u00f6z\u00fcm var:\r\n\r\n* Eski nesil: Vuex\r\n* Modern ve hafif: **Pinia**\r\n\r\n\u00d6rne\u011fin Pinia ile \u00e7ok basit bir store:\r\n\r\n```js\r\n// stores/counter.js\r\nimport { defineStore } from \"pinia\";\r\n\r\nexport const useCounterStore = defineStore(\"counter\", {\r\n  state: () => ({\r\n    count: 0,\r\n  }),\r\n  actions: {\r\n    increment() {\r\n      this.count++;\r\n    },\r\n  },\r\n});\r\n```\r\n\r\nComponent i\u00e7inde kullan\u0131m\u0131:\r\n\r\n```vue\r\n<script setup>\r\nimport { useCounterStore } from \"@/stores/counter\";\r\n\r\nconst counter = useCounterStore();\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<template>\r\n  <div>\r\n    <p>Counter: {{ counter.count }}</p>\r\n    <button @click=\"counter.increment()\">+1</button>\r\n  </div>\r\n</template>\r\n```\r\n\r\nBurada olan \u015fey asl\u0131nda:\r\n\r\n* JavaScript ile global bir \u201cstate objesi\u201d olu\u015fturuyorsun\r\n* Vue ve Pinia bunu reaktif hale getirip component\u2019lerle ba\u011flayor\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## JavaScript + Vue ile \u00c7al\u0131\u015f\u0131rken Dikkat Etmen Gereken Noktalar\r\n\r\n1. **JS Temelini Hafife Alma**\r\n   Vue, JavaScript\u2019i saklam\u0131yor, aksine **daha \u00e7ok kullanman\u0131** sa\u011fl\u0131yor.\r\n   Ne kadar iyi JS bilirsen, Vue ile o kadar rahat edersin.\r\n\r\n2. **Reaktivite Mant\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 Anla**\r\n   Vue\u2019da \u201cde\u011fi\u015fken de\u011fi\u015ftirdim, DOM otomatik g\u00fcncellendi\u201d b\u00fcy\u00fc gibi gelebilir.\r\n   Ama bunun arkas\u0131nda reaktivite sistemi var. \u00d6zellikle `ref`, `reactive`, `computed`, `watch` gibi kavramlar\u0131 sindir.\r\n\r\n3. **Component Mant\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 Benimse**\r\n   Bir sayfay\u0131:\r\n\r\n   * Header component\r\n   * Sidebar component\r\n   * Content component\r\n   * Footer component\r\n     gibi par\u00e7alara ay\u0131rmak, hem JS hem HTML taraf\u0131nda temiz bir yap\u0131 sa\u011flar.\r\n\r\n4. **Temiz Dosya Yap\u0131s\u0131 Kur**\r\n   API servislerini `services/`, global state\u2019i `stores/`, reusable component\u2019leri `components/` dizinine al.\r\n   Bu asl\u0131nda JavaScript mod\u00fcllerini mant\u0131kl\u0131 klas\u00f6rlere ay\u0131rmaktan ibaret.\r\n\r\n5. **TypeScript D\u00fc\u015f\u00fcn (\u0130leri Seviyede)**\r\n   Vue, TypeScript ile \u00e7ok iyi \u00e7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor. JavaScript temelin oturduktan sonra TS \u00f6\u011frenmek, \u00f6zellikle b\u00fcy\u00fck projelerde sana ciddi g\u00fc\u00e7 kazand\u0131r\u0131r.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Nereden Ba\u015flamal\u0131?\r\n\r\nBa\u015flang\u0131\u00e7 i\u00e7in \u00f6neri yol haritas\u0131:\r\n\r\n1. **Saf JavaScript ile mini projeler yap**\r\n\r\n   * Todo list\r\n   * Basit fetch ile API\u2019den veri \u00e7ekip listeleme\r\n   * Modal a\u00e7-kapat\r\n\r\n2. **Vue\u2019yu CDN ile dene**\r\n\r\n   * Tek HTML dosyas\u0131nda Vue ekle\r\n   * `data`, `methods`, `v-for`, `v-if`, `v-model` gibi temel direktifleri kullan\r\n\r\n3. **Vite ile Vue 3 projesi a\u00e7**\r\n\r\n   ```bash\r\n   npm create vite@latest my-vue-app -- --template vue\r\n   cd my-vue-app\r\n   npm install\r\n   npm run dev\r\n   ```\r\n\r\n4. **Component ve `script setup` yap\u0131s\u0131na al\u0131\u015f**\r\n\r\n   * K\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck component\u2019ler yaz\r\n   * Props ve emit (event) kullan\r\n\r\n5. **Pinia ile basit bir global state yaz**\r\n\r\n   * Login state, counter, theme vs. gibi basit \u015feylerle ba\u015fla\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Son S\u00f6z\r\n\r\nJavaScript ve Vue ili\u015fkisi asl\u0131nda \u015fu \u015fekilde \u00f6zetlenebilir:\r\n\r\n> JavaScript, beynin. Vue, o beyni kullanarak **d\u00fczenli, reaktif, component tabanl\u0131** aray\u00fczler \u00e7izmeni sa\u011flayan iskelet.\r\n\r\nJS temelin ne kadar sa\u011flam olursa, Vue \u00f6\u011frenmek ve \u00f6zellikle ileri seviye \u00f6zelliklerine (Composition API, Pinia, Router, SSR, PWA vs.) ge\u00e7mek o kadar h\u0131zl\u0131 olur.\n\n        Soru: {question}\n        Cevap:"}, {"role": "user", "content": "question faruk \u015feker kimdir ?"}, {"role": "ai", "content": "### Faruk \u015eeker Kimdir?\n\nFaruk \u015eeker, **mid-level full-stack yaz\u0131l\u0131m geli\u015ftiricisi**. A\u011f\u0131rl\u0131kl\u0131 **Python/Django** backend uzman\u0131, yapay zeka ve web uygulamalar\u0131yla g\u00fcnl\u00fck hayat\u0131/i\u015f s\u00fcre\u00e7lerini kolayla\u015ft\u0131ran \u00e7\u00f6z\u00fcmler \u00fcretiyor.\n\n#### Kariyer:\n- **2024'ten beri freelance**: Web geli\u015ftirme, veri madencili\u011fi, scraping, bot y\u00f6netimi, otomasyon (\u00e7e\u015fitli sekt\u00f6rler).\n- **D\u00f6kta\u015f**: HR i\u00e7in meslek hastal\u0131klar\u0131 app'i ve dahili numara arama